data.description: Elegance abounds in this fabulous  3 bedroom, 3 full bath home.  Coastal inspired vibes resonate throughout the home with many upgrades that include but are not limited to; quartz countertops in kitchen and baths, 9' sliding glass door at the dining area, screened porch/lanai area, gourmet kitchen layout, upgraded cabinetry, pendant and under counter lighting, upgraded carpet and padding throughout the loft area.  Four Seasons Community offers resort style living right here in Maryland.   Clubhouse, party rooms, fitness center, pool, pickle ball, tennis, bocce courts, marina and much more.  clubhouse is open for tour 9-5 pm daily.  Please see movie camera icon for video and please see the paper icon for documents inclusive of floor plan, cable and internet upgrades and upgraded features of this home.
